<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Competitor Price API Documentation</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>This API provides simulated competitor pricing data. Prices fluctuate based on a daily bell curve with a peak at 2 PM.</p>
        <h2>API Endpoints</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>GET /prices</strong> - Retrieves current prices and inventory. Requires an API key.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Usage</h2>
        <p>To use this API, include the API key as a query parameter like so: <code>?api_key=demo123</code></p>
    </section>
